SPARKLE OF HOPE tracked along the inside, wisely tipped out to take aim outside of the leading pair approaching the five sixteenths pole, ranged up to bid in the four path entering the lane, but failed to keep pace with an inner counterpart in upper stretch and chased that one home to prove second best. PROMISE OF HOPE tracked three wide, chased into the turn, yielded between horses after being floated four wide nearing the five sixteenths pole, yet regained stride among foes while tipping to the five path in midstretch, gained show in the final furlong but was caught by an inner bidder late. MISS FOXANN bumped an outer rival with eleven sixteenths to go, pursued from off of the pace in the three path, moved between horses entering the lane and chased evenly thereafter. PUNCHY GIRL broke a step slow, laid off of the pace along the inside into the turn, shifted out turning for home, tipped from the five path to the six path in upper stretch, stayed on outside of rivals, attempted a bid for minor placings in the final furlong but leveled off. MOON MAGIC CHRISSY set the pace along the inside, but was headed by a pair of outer bidders entering the lane and weakened on her left lead. VOW tracked two wide and between horses, cut the corner turning for home and faded. ARDEN'S ASSAULT took contact from an inner rival nearing the eleven sixteenths pole, chased from midpack four to five wide and faded between horses in upper stretch. MUSIC FESTIVAL leaned inwardly while off a step slow at the start, lacked speed in the three path, swung to the seven path entering the lane and made little impact.
